<%= base_prompt %>

=== PASS 2: FINAL WRITING ===
Use this approved structure plan and keep its section order.

<%= structure_json %>

Writing constraints:
- Preserve section order and intent from the structure plan.
- Preserve contract-required links/headings/code density.
- Keep citations and audit_notes grounded in source modules/files.
- Produce final publication-ready content (not an outline).
- Use these exact required section headings (do not rename or merge):
<%= Enum.map_join(required_sections, "\n", fn heading -> "- " <> heading end) %>
- Target <%= min_words %>-<%= max_words %> words in `body_markdown`.
- If draft is short, expand with concrete examples, troubleshooting, and verification details from source snippets.
